title: 5 True Cases That Occurred In Every Season Of "American Horror Story"
author: Top 5 Unknowns
comment: ahs is such a well put together show. it isnt just some cheesy scary horror series. it has meaning & is actually meant to entertain and make you overthink society.
Season five was really about HH Holmes and his hotel

Another interesting thing about the Cecil (now the stay on main) around the time Elisa Lam was in the water tank there was a Tuberculosis outbreak among the homeless near the Cecil. The test they used was called Lam Elisa.
The way you pronounce “Coven”. The correct pronunciation rhymes with “Oven”
The ghosts of all the serial killers came to the hotel on Halloween night. They did not all happen to check in at the same time
